data.description: ADORABLE RAISED RANCH IN PRIME LOCATION CLOSE TO SHOPS, RESTAURANTS, SCHOOLS, MEDICAL, & MORE!  Enjoy being 5 minutes from everything but feeling like you are tucked away in your own peaceful retreat.  Your dream home awaits on this quiet cul-de-sac property featuring 3 beds, 1 full bath, & a finished lower level.  Welcome guests with your well-manicured front yard & captivating curb appeal.  Situated on a lovely half-acre property, a fenced-in backyard, 1 car garage, and an outdoor back deck overlooking your backyard is the perfect place to host family gatherings.  Inside a modern color palette, original hardwoods, central A/C, natural gas, and a pellet stove are just some of the upgrades you will enjoy.  Your kitchen features white cabinets, SS appliances, & plenty of work space.  Enjoy having the bedrooms on the main level.  A huge finished lower level provides tons of options for a rec room, guest suite,  home office, gym & more.  FREE 1-YR WARRANTY FOR THE BUYER!
